                "key": "Tutorial",
                "string_values": [
                  "Elemental creatures who protect themselves from incoming attack with their durable shell. Find an opportune moment to land a blow to their <span style=\"color:#FFE14BFF\">elemental core</span>. They are able to control their <span style=\"color:#FFE14BFF\">elemental orb</span> in fights and restore their health when they feel threatened. If you fail to utilize the upcurrents to absorb these orbs, the battle will be significantly harder."
